column5: Wow 80 degrees and sunny dam near all week up by Nestorfalls. Myself i would prefer it a little cooler than that........LOL.
Been pretty warm in the area for sure.water temps are on the rise.
Water temps aren't the only temps on the rise,my temps on the rise from not being there with you john so you could net my fish haha

Ì hear you.Love netting fish.Getting lots of practise this week.lol.Maybe tomorrow we will get out on Cedar and see how crappie bite is.Thinking back baysxmight be warm enough to get them going.Usually need 60+f for them to move in.Should be close with warm temps weve had.Got 2 rods rigģed up with slip bobbers.Of course cant pass up tge walleye spots we will be going by.lol.
Well be sure torture us Americans with more pictures,I'm assuming after tomorrow there will be pictures,good luck I'm not sure if you need it or not,rod
